{"TopicId":77809,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Hinges..","CreatedByName":"Hacktech","CreatedById":57094,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T10:22:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Hacktech","CreatedById":57094,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T10:22:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHey! \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027d like to know if anyone knows how to make hinges from the stock items in ksp?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"robopilot99","CreatedById":102126,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T10:48:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf I remember correctly the structural pylon bends a ton.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qazsedcft","CreatedById":114699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T11:49:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe only way I know is using the claw but it\u0027s large and clunky. Basically, between two flat pieces you put the claw on one end and docking ports on the other end. Then you arm the claw and undock the ports. Use landing struts and RCS to control the thing.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Monkeh","CreatedById":72122,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T12:11:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI saw a video once where someone used landing legs and 2x2 panels and made a cargo bay out of that, which was a hinged row of panels that opened with the gears opening. If that\u0027s in any way helpful then you\u0027re a better person than me.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou do about the infernal robotics mod right? Really great work there.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-07-17T08:22:10Z\u0022 title=\u002207/17/2014 08:22  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 17, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Monkeh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p331083","CreatedById":57783,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T12:34:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBack a few versions ago(.19 i think) you could use the medium struts as hinges with the panels \u002B docking ports. No longer works.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sirine","CreatedById":74830,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-16T13:22:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/XwCRbfk4sXE?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/fgdFr1QvI4o?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThis might give you some ideal.\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-07-16T13:24:41Z\u0022 title=\u002207/16/2014 01:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 16, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Sirine\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}